<p><span class="flagicon"><a href="Ottoman_Empire" title="Ottoman Empire"><img alt="Ottoman Empire" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/Ottoman_flag.svg/22px-Ottoman_flag.svg.png" width="22" height="15" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/Ottoman_flag.svg/33px-Ottoman_flag.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b0/Ottoman_flag.svg/44px-Ottoman_flag.svg.png 2x" /></a></span> 2,998,321</p>
