<th width="10%">Number of troops deployed on Ottomans fronts<sup id="cite_ref-Brief_Ottoman_History_77-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Brief_Ottoman_History-77"><span>[</span>77<span>]</span></a></sup></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="Great_Britain" title="Great Britain">Great Britain</a></td>
<td>2,550,000 men deployed (32% of the total <a href="British_armed_forces" title="British armed forces" class="mw-redirect">British armed forces</a>), at one point 880,300 British soldiers were fighting the Ottomans (24% of total.)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="Russian_Empire" title="Russian Empire">Russian Empire</a></td>
<td>702,000 men (19% of total army) were fighting the Ottomans in the <a href="Caucasus_Front" title="Caucasus Front" class="mw-redirect">Caucasus Front</a> by September 1916.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="France" title="France">France</a></td>
