<li id="cite_note-18"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFShapiro2006">Shapiro 2006</a>, p.&#160;329 citing a wire service report in <i>The Indianapolis Star, 20 September 1914</i></span></li>
